  "summary": "This document is an official call for applications issued by an Italian educational authority for the assignment of scholarships related to the right to university education for the academic year 2025/2026. Its main purpose is to establish the rules, eligibility criteria, and procedures for awarding financial support to students based on their financial situation and academic merit. Key topics covered include definitions, eligible student categories, application deadlines and procedures, financial assessment criteria (I.S.E.E.), merit evaluation, ranking formation, payment methods, conditions for scholarship forfeiture, and provisions for international mobility and foreign students.",
